<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>[AUTOR NAME] – [BUCHTITEL]</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --accent: #b5472a;
    --accent-light: #f4e8e3;
    --ink: #1f1c1a;
    --paper: #fdfbf8;
    --muted: #8a8378;
    --placeholder-bg: repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      #eee0d8,
      #eee0d8 10px,
      #f6ece5 10px,
      #f6ece5 20px
    );
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .template-banner {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .template-banner strong { color: #f0c14b; }

  .wrap {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* Header */
  header {
    padding: 56px 0 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 96px;
    height: 96px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 18px;
    background: var(--placeholder-bg);
    border: 2px dashed #c9b8ab;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4px;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  header p.claim {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* Book section */
  .book {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 0 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #ece3da;
  }

  .cover {
    width: 168px;
    height: 240px;
    background: var(--placeholder-bg);
    border: 2px dashed #c9b8ab;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .book h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .book .subtitle {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .book .description {
    font-size: 15px;
    max-width: 420px;
    color: #4a4640;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .price .placeholder-tag {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .buy-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(181, 71, 42, 0.25);
  }

  .buy-btn:hover {
    background: #983a22;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .buy-note {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Social proof */
  .proof {
    padding: 36px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #ece3da;
  }

  .proof h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .quote {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-left: 3px dashed var(--accent);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #4a3a32;
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  }

  .quote .who {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    padding: 32px 0 56px;
    border-top: 1px solid #ece3da;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .socials {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .social-dot {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--placeholder-bg);
    border: 2px dashed #c9b8ab;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  footer .legal {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  footer .legal a {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    header { padding: 40px 0 24px; }
    .book { padding: 20px 0 32px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="template-banner">
    <strong>VORLAGE</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="wrap">

    <header>
      <div class="avatar">[AUTOR<br>FOTO]</div>
      <h1>[Autor:in Name]</h1>
      <p class="claim">[Kurzer Claim]</p>
    </header>

    <section class="book">
      <div class="cover">[BUCHCOVER<br>PLATZHALTER]</div>
      <h2>[Buchtitel]</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">[Untertitel]</p>
      <p class="description">
        [2–3 Sätze Beschreibung: worum geht es im Buch, warum sollte man es lesen.
        Platzhaltertext — durch eigene Buchbeschreibung ersetzen.]
      </p>

      <div class="price">
        [€XX,XX]
      </div>

      <a href="#" class="buy-btn">Jetzt im Shop kaufen</a>
    </section>

    <section class="proof">
      <h3>Leser:innen-Stimmen</h3>
      <div class="quote">
        „[Platzhalter-Zitat]"
        <span class="who">— [Name / Quelle]</span>
      </div>
      <div class="quote">
        „[Platzhalter-Zitat]"
        <span class="who">— [Name / Quelle]</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div class="socials">
        <div class="social-dot">IG</div>
        <div class="social-dot">TT</div>
        <div class="social-dot">FB</div>
      </div>
      <p class="legal">
        [Verlag/Autor Name] · <a href="#">Impressum</a> · <a href="#">Datenschutz</a>
      </p>
    </footer>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
